%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e7a5919ff3dd728499db3d01b9c7d9c4, type: 3}
  m_Name: Level1IntroBeforeTrainSequence
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - text: So you're the new hire in town huh? Welcome to RouterCo, where we route
      information between towns and make sure it's safe for our company.
    speakerName: Sheriff
    portrait: {fileID: -7307842283543146795, guid: 8e858e9d9926f124392468c068f061d7, type: 3}
    useCustomRevealSpeed: 0
    revealLettersPerSecond: 0
    interactionRequirement:
      enabled: 0
      allowedInteractionIds: []
      requiredInteractionCount: 1
  - text: Now buckle up 'cause I'm only gonna say this once.
    speakerName: Sheriff
    portrait: {fileID: -7307842283543146795, guid: 8e858e9d9926f124392468c068f061d7, type: 3}
    useCustomRevealSpeed: 0
    revealLettersPerSecond: 0
    interactionRequirement:
      enabled: 0
      allowedInteractionIds: []
      requiredInteractionCount: 1
  - text: 'We''ve got scheduled trains coming in with lots of different info. You''ll
      have to let ''em pass or send ''em back based on what we''re expecting. '
    speakerName: Sheriff
    portrait: {fileID: -7307842283543146795, guid: 8e858e9d9926f124392468c068f061d7, type: 3}
    useCustomRevealSpeed: 0
    revealLettersPerSecond: 0
    interactionRequirement:
      enabled: 0
      allowedInteractionIds: []
      requiredInteractionCount: 1
  - text: I'll show you the ropes for today, but afterwards you're on your own!
    speakerName: Sheriff
    portrait: {fileID: -7307842283543146795, guid: 8e858e9d9926f124392468c068f061d7, type: 3}
    useCustomRevealSpeed: 0
    revealLettersPerSecond: 0
    interactionRequirement:
      enabled: 0
      allowedInteractionIds: []
      requiredInteractionCount: 1
  - text: 'When a train comes in you need to check two things for each type of request:
      the type of request and the user input'
    speakerName: Sheriff
    portrait: {fileID: -7307842283543146795, guid: 8e858e9d9926f124392468c068f061d7, type: 3}
    useCustomRevealSpeed: 0
    revealLettersPerSecond: 0
    interactionRequirement:
      enabled: 0
      allowedInteractionIds: []
      requiredInteractionCount: 1
  - text: Here comes the train now, pay attention.
    speakerName: Sheriff
    portrait: {fileID: -7307842283543146795, guid: 8e858e9d9926f124392468c068f061d7, type: 3}
    useCustomRevealSpeed: 0
    revealLettersPerSecond: 0
    interactionRequirement:
      enabled: 0
      allowedInteractionIds: []
      requiredInteractionCount: 1
